NOVEMBER 7 - RALLY in CONCORD
--------------------------------------------
On Saturday November 7th at 2:00 PM Organizing for America and other pro-government health care astroturfed groups will gather in front of the State House in Concord to hear from Representative Carol Shea-Porter, Mrs. Peggo Hodes, and NHDP Chairman Raymond Buckley and others about the "need for speedy and responsible health insurance reform for New Hampshire".

Saturday looks to be a sunny day. Consider providing them a welcoming committee.
Bring appropriate signs.

Saturday, November 7 from 2:00 PM - 4:00 PM
NH State House (Concord, NH)
107 N. Main St.
Concord, NH 03301
item.name: Anti-CommieCare Rally in Concord, NH
